# PLACEHOLDER: Architecture Diagram

## Instructions to Generate

This file is a placeholder for the system architecture diagram. Replace it with an actual PNG image.

### Recommended Tools

1. **Draw.io / diagrams.net** (free, web-based)
   - Open https://app.diagrams.net
   - Create a new diagram
   - Export as PNG (recommended: 2x resolution)
   - Save as `architecture.png` in this directory

2. **Mermaid CLI** (if you prefer code-based diagrams)
   ```bash
   npm install -g @mermaid-js/mermaid-cli
   mmdc -i architecture.mmd -o architecture.png -w 2000
   ```

### Suggested Architecture Diagram Content

The diagram should show:

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     CLIENT LAYER                            │
│   Web App (React)     │    Admin Dashboard     │    CLI     │
└──────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────┘
                               │ HTTPS
┌──────────────────────────────v──────────────────────────────┐
│                    API GATEWAY                              │
│              (Go, NGINX, Rate Limiter)                      │
└──┬──────────┬──────────┬──────────┬──────────┬──────────┬──┘
   │          │          │          │          │          │
   v          v          v          v          v          v
┌──────┐ ┌──────┐ ┌──────┐ ┌──────┐ ┌──────┐ ┌──────┐
│ User │ │Resume│ │Inter │ │  AI  │ │Score │ │Admin │
│ Svc  │ │ Svc  │ │  Svc │ │ Svc  │ │ Svc  │ │ Svc  │
│ (Go) │ │ (Go) │ │ (Go) │ │(Py)  │ │(Py)  │ │ (Go) │
└──┬───┘ └──┬───┘ └──┬───┘ └──┬───┘ └──┬───┘ └──┬───┘
   │         │        │        │        │        │
   v         v        v        v        v        v
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                  DATA / INFRASTRUCTURE                      │
│  PostgreSQL (per svc) │ Redis │ Kafka │ S3 │ Jaeger/Prom   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### File Requirements

- **Format:** PNG
- **Resolution:** Minimum 1920x1080
- **Style:** Clean, labeled boxes with clear service names and technology tags
- **Color coding:** Use different colors for Go services vs Python services
